| *Field-by-field spec for Rejuvenate Skin Experts*                     |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

This document specifies every field, conditional logic rule, and
contraindication mapping needed to build the digital consultation and
consent form system for Rejuvenate Skin Experts. It covers two form
types: the Client Consultation Form (completed once, reviewed
periodically) and Treatment-Specific Consent Forms (signed per
treatment/course).

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Logic Key:** **BLOCK** = auto-prevents booking for that treatment \|
  **FLAG** = warns therapist, requires manual override \| **SHOW** =
  reveals conditional follow-up fields

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

**Form 1: Client Consultation Form**

*Completed by every new client before their first treatment. Reviewed
and re-signed every 6 months or if medical circumstances change. GDPR
special category data --- requires explicit consent, 6-year minimum
retention.*

